14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 397 of Title 59, unless there is
17 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 This section shall modify the Oklahoma Administrative Code
19 Section 235:10-11-1 by the following provisions:
20 1. Penalties for vendor payments may only be imposed after a
21 formal court judgment;
22 2. Penalties may only be imposed on funeral establishments and
23 may not be imposed against the Funeral Director in Charge;
