1 3. These rules are only applicable to active funeral
2 establishments;
3 4. All funeral establishments must be in compliance with
4 federal bankruptcy laws; and
5 5. All cash payments made in advance must meet the requirements
6 of consumer fund receipts.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
